      *OET do file
*By Phil Tian

clear all

cd E:/

capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

gen double ps=psexpectation/1000

program define OET_ML

args lnf sigma k
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`k')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')

end
